quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  43,34,"Walibuyootihim abwaban wasururanAAalayha yattaki-oon"
  43,35,"Wazukhrufan wa-in kullu thalika lammamataAAu alhayati addunya wal-akhiratuAAinda rabbika lilmuttaqeen"
  43,36,"Waman yaAAshu AAan thikri arrahmaninuqayyid lahu shaytanan fahuwa lahu qareen"
  43,37,"Wa-innahum layasuddoonahum AAani assabeeliwayahsaboona annahum muhtadoon"
  43,38,"Hatta itha jaanaqala ya layta baynee wabaynaka buAAda almashriqaynifabi/sa alqareen"
  43,39,"Walan yanfaAAakumu alyawma ith thalamtumannakum fee alAAathabi mushtarikoon"
  43,40,"Afaanta tusmiAAu assumma awtahdee alAAumya waman kana fee dalalinmubeen"
  43,41,"Fa-imma nathhabanna bikafa-inna minhum muntaqimoon"
  43,42,"Aw nuriyannaka allathee waAAadnahumfa-inna AAalayhim muqtadiroon"
  43,43,"Fastamsik billatheeoohiya ilayka innaka AAala siratinmustaqeem"
  43,44,"Wa-innahu lathikrun laka waliqawmikawasawfa tus-aloon"
  43,45,"Was-al man arsalna minqablika min rusulina ajaAAalna min dooni arrahmanialihatan yuAAbadoon"
  43,46,"Walaqad arsalna moosa bi-ayatinaila firAAawna wamala-ihi faqala innee rasoolu rabbialAAalameen"
  43,47,"Falamma jaahum bi-ayatinaitha hum minha yadhakoon"
